Package fi.tuni.cezaro

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommentRepository
    Comment repository implementation for handling Comment table that extends from CrudRepository.
    PostRepository
    Post repository implementation for handling Post table that extends from CrudRepository.
    UserReporistory
    User repository implementation for handling Userx table that extends from CrudRepository.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlogApplication
    Main class for starting SpringBootApplication.
    CezaroApplicationTests  
    Comment
    Entity class that is used to define and save post comment data in database.
    CommentController
    RestController to handle Comment entity saving, delete and updating to database.
    Post
    Entity class that is used to define and save Blog post data in database.
    PostController
    RestController to handle Post entity saving, delete and updating to database.
    User
    Entity class that is used to define and save username and password in database.
    UserController
    RestController to handle creating and deleting User entity from database.
